// Template for your personal signing config.
//
// Setup (one time):
//   1. cp LocalTeam.xcconfig.example LocalTeam.xcconfig
//   2. Set DEVELOPMENT_TEAM below to your 10-character Apple Development Team id
//      (Xcode ▸ Settings ▸ Accounts ▸ your team, or developer.apple.com → Membership).
//   3. Build. LocalTeam.xcconfig is gitignored and pulled in via Local.xcconfig's optional
//      #include, so your team id never lands in the tracked Cotabby.xcodeproj.
//
// Why this exists: project.yml deliberately does NOT hardcode a team, so Xcode's automatic
// signing reads it from here instead of rewriting project.pbxproj on every build.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
